        "summary":  "AWS launched Amazon Bedrock Managed Knowledge Base in general availability, a fully managed service that simplifies enterprise search for AI agents by handling data ingestion, storage, and retrieval without requiring manual infrastructure setup. The service features native connectors to popular enterprise platforms, intelligent multimodal document parsing, and two retrieval modes ΓÇö standard retrieve for direct lookups and agentic retrieval for complex multi-hop reasoning.",
