        "summary":  "The article argues that performance per watt is the most critical efficiency metric for AI infrastructure because power constraints directly determine revenue and profitability in AI factories. NVIDIA\u0027s Blackwell NVL72 platform achieves up to 25x better performance per watt compared to Hopper when serving mixture-of-experts models across a 72-GPU domain.",
